n'*m* v*r*d* l*rg*, *ntr* q**nt**s, d*sc*nd* p*l* p*nd*r d* c*ll*n*, m*s
*cc*ss*v*l * c*rr**g*ns; * *h*, n'*m r*c*nt*, l*d**d* d* m*r*s,
