*p*rt* d* mã*, p*ss**-lh* * br*ç* p*l* c*nt*, ch*m**-lh* * s** q**r*d*
M***. * c*nd*ss* s*rr**, c*m * *lh*r **nd* h*m*d*, *m r*st* d* p*ll*d*z,
m*v*nd* * l*q** l*ng**d*m*nt*, r*c*st*d* *m d**s *lm*f*d*s d*
s*ph*--d*b**x* d* b*st* d* m*r*d* q** *rg*** * fr*nt* *nsp*r*d*.




