d* c**p*, f*rr*d* d* n*gr*, d*st*c*v* *m p*rf*l cl*r* d'*st*t**, *m t*m
*nd**d* d* c*b*ll* l**r*. C*rl*s t*r** pr*f*nd*m*nt* * ch*p**, tã*
p*rt*rb*d*, q** *s s**s p*ss*s h*s*t*r*m. _*ll*_ *b**x** * c*b*ç*, d*
