R*c*lh*r*m p*l* *sc*d* p*rt*c*l*r d* C*rl*s--q** M*r** *ch*v*
«myst*r**s*» c*m *q**ll*s v*ll*d*s gr*ss*s côr d* c*r*j*, f*rr*nd*-*
c*m* *m c*fr*, * *b*f*nd* t*d* * r*m*r d* s***s. C*rl*s j*r** q** n*nc*
