n*s l*nç**s, g*z*nd* *q**ll* b*c*d* d* c*l*r * d* c*nchêg* *nt*s d'*r
*ffr*nt*r fór* *s *m*rg*r*s d* d**.

* p**c* * p**c*, s*b * t*p*d* c*nchêg* d*s c*b*rt*r*s *m q** s*
