l*g*l*d*d*--d* n*d* q** r*cl*m*ss* * *xp*r**nc** d'*m pr*c*r*d*r. *r*
*p*n*s *ntr*d*z*r *m b*rg**z m**s n'*m s*gr*d* tã* t*rr*v*lm*nt*
