* q** * T*v**r* f*ll** *m *rm*s c*m *m*s r*p*r*g*s...

C*rl*s *nc*lh** *s h*mbr*s c*m h*rr*r. Q** s*rd*d*z, *r c*m m*lh*r*s
p*r* C*ntr*, d* d**!... D* n**t*, n*s tr*v*s, p*r b*b*d**r*, v*... M*s *
