d* C*rl*s, * N*w-Y*rk c*b*rt* d* n*v* s*b *m s*l r*t*l*nt*. *
*cr*sc*nt*v* **nd*: «*st*-s* *p*ss*nd* d* nós * *mbr**g**z d*s v**g*ns,
