*rm*n** * p*l* Syr**, d*sc*r ** *gypt* * r*t*mp*r*r-n*s n* s*gr*d* N*l*;
s*b*r d*p**s * *th*n*s, l*nç*r s*br* * *cr*p*l* *m* s**d*çã* * M*n*rv*;
p*ss*r * N*p*l*s; d*r *m *lh*r * *rg*l** * * M*rr*c*s; * c*h*r *mf*m **
c*mpr*d* *m S*nt* *l*v** l* p*r* *s m**d*s d* 79 * d*sc*nç*r *s m*mbr*s
